{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"ARIA","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/ARIA","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>ARIA</strong>（Accessible Rich <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Internet\">Internet <small>(en-US)</small></a> Applications，可訪問的富網際網路應用程式）是一個 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C</a> 規範，用已對 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> 添加語義和元數據，以迎合需要輔助技術的用戶。</p>\n<p>例如：你可以給一個 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Tag\">標籤 <small>(en-US)</small></a>添加 <code>role=\"alert\"</code> 屬性提醒視覺障礙用戶，這裏的訊息很重要並對時間敏感（針對非視覺障礙用戶，你可能本來會用文字顔色傳達這種事）。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA\">ARIA</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"ARIA（Accessible Rich Internet (en-US) Applications，可訪問的富網際網路應用程式）是一個 W3C 規範，用已對 HTML 添加語義和元數據，以迎合需要輔助技術的用戶。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"ARIA","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"ARIA","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"ARIA","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"ARIA","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"ARIA","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"ARIA","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/aria","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/aria/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.m